# 🌞 Automated Solar Grass Cutter with Sun Tracking System

## 📌 Description
The Automated Solar Grass Cutter with Sun Tracking System is an eco-friendly and energy-efficient robotic system designed for automatic grass cutting using solar power. The system integrates a sun tracking mechanism to maximize solar energy harvesting throughout the day, ensuring efficient battery charging and continuous operation.

The solar panel is mounted on a tracking mechanism that automatically adjusts its position based on sunlight direction. The stored solar energy is used to power the cutting motor, enabling fully automated grass cutting without human intervention.

This system combines renewable energy, automation, and embedded control to reduce manual effort and promote sustainable technology.

